## Build Log — Progress So Far

**Project Name:** `aws-cicd-monitor`  
**Stack:** Python Flask → GitHub Actions → AWS EC2 + CloudWatch + SNS  
**Goal:** Every `git push` triggers build → test → deploy → monitor → alert

